rights watch is a private organization that monitors rights 
violations worldwide 
iraq is a wellorganized police state and its government is 
one of the most brutal and repressive regimes in power today 
said korn 
president bush has strongly condemned saddam in recent days he 
halted trade with iraq and sent troops to saudi arabia in response 
