the military cousin of the boeing 707 airliner are a vital link in 
the quick deployment of men and material to the persian gulf 
all combat aircraft and many of the transports flying to the 
middle east are potential receivers that need to be dragged 
across the pond air force lexicon for airtoair refueling over 
the atlantic 
there arent too many missions that can take place in the air 
force without a kc135 said the tankers pilot whose husband 
also flies the venerable aircraft 
the tankers crew of two men and two women was proud of their 
