<TEXT>
the dollar sank to another alltime low friday 
against the german mark and fell against most other major 
currencies reflecting continuing pessimism about the state of the 
us economy 
gold prices were mixed after gold posted gains in other 
markets republic national bank in new york quoted an afterhours 
bid of 40850 a troy ounce as of 4 pm edt down 50 cents from 
thursdays late bid 
